  "texts": [
    "However, experimental work demonstrates that ethanol can actually accelerate fuel ignition at relatively high pressures, in agreement with our simulation results 57.",
    "Extended Data Fig. 3 provides further justification for the ANI-1xnr ethanol simulation results.",
    "Emerging research has shown the success of application-specific MLIPs on systems such as radical reactions in hydrocarbon combustion and well-known gas-phase mechanisms 58, 59.",
    "Zeng et al.",
    "24 trained an NN-based potential to a dataset of QM-calculated fragment clusters sampled from a ReaxFF simulation of the combustion process of a mixture of CH 4 and O 2."
